                            <img src="images/budgie-home.png" class="preview"/>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="container">
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-md-6">
                    <h2>Spend Confidently</h2>
                    <p>Say goodbye to the stress and guilt surrounding your bank statements. Budgie's simple daily allowance makes purchasing decisions a breeze. Do you have enough today? Buy that orange mocha frappuccino! Not quite? Wait 'til you get more allowance tomorrow.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-6">
                    <h2>Financial Awareness</h2>
                    <p>Checking Budgie every day will keep you totally aware of your spending habits. Suddenly you'll find yourself looking forward to purchases with excitement rather than backward with regret.  </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div id="additional-features" class="container">
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-md-4">
                    <div class="video-overlay left">
                        <video width="252" height="auto" loop="" autoplay="">
                          <source src="/media/budgie-save.webm" type="video/webm">
                          <source src="/media/budgie-home.mp4" type="video/mp4">
                        </video>
                        <img src="images/budgie-save.png" class="preview preview-left"/>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-8">
                    <h2>Saving is fun now!</h2>
                    <p>When you've got a little extra allowance at the end of the day, save it!</p>
                    <p>At any time, contribute to one of your financial savings goals and see the effects in real time! Budgie gives you total control over your finances, whether your money's in your wallet or in your bank.</p>
                    <p>It feels great to accomplish goals, and Budgie is here for just that.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
